 
<p>
<a href="https://www.theguardian.com/world/2023/apr/08/iranian-police-plan-to-use-smart-cameras-to-identify-violators-of-hijab-law">Iran is using facial recognition</a>
in public places to identify
the dangerous criminals that don't wear required Islamic clothing.
<p>
They have been specifically
<a href="https://www.theguardian.com/world/2023/apr/10/women-not-wearing-hijab-to-be-banned-from-tehran-metro-reports">banned from the Tehram Metro</a>.

